**Text Styles:** All text styles (heading, subtitle, paragraph, link) use `font.principal` (Ubuntu) as configured in lines 165-430.

### 3. Current Storybook Configuration

**Main Config File:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/.storybook/main.ts`
- Lines 1-2: Framework is `@storybook/react-native-web-vite`
- Lines 186-198: Module transpilation includes `@semparar/design-system-app`
